OL,3,CStormont Health Minister orders pay
OL,4,Cincrease totalling around #200 million
OL,6,FStormont Health Minister Mike Nesbitt
OL,7,Fsaid he has signed a pay increase for
OL,8,Fworkers, despite not having the budget
OL,9,Fto cover it.
OL,11,FHe said the salary increase
OL,12,Frecommended totalled around #200
OL,13,Fmillion in Northern Ireland, including
OL,14,F3.6% for nurses and staff under Agenda
OL,15,Ffor Change, 4% for doctors, and 4%
OL,16,Fplus #750 for resident doctors `
OL,17,Fformerly known as junior doctors.
