OL,3,CStormont Health Minister orders pay
OL,4,Cincrease totalling around #200 million
OL,6,FIt comes after recommendations were
OL,7,Fannounced earlier by pay review
OL,8,Fbodies, including 3.6% for health
OL,9,Fworkers and 4% for doctors.
OL,11,FMr Nesbitt said he expects to have to
OL,12,Fissue a ministerial directive, which
OL,13,Fwill go to the Finance Minister, John
OL,14,FO'Dowd, and potentially be passed to
OL,15,Fthe Executive for approval.
