OL,3,CStormont Health Minister orders pay
OL,4,Cincrease totalling around #200 million
OL,6,FSpeaking to media at the Department of
OL,7,FHealth headquarters in Belfast on
OL,8,FThursday afternoon, Mr Nesbitt said he
OL,9,Fwas very unhappy last year when health
OL,10,Fworkers had to wait until the end of
OL,11,Fthe financial year for confirmation
OL,12,Fthat they were going to get their pay
OL,13,Fparity recommendation implemented.
OL,15,F"I said I wanted it to be the last
OL,16,Ftime and I'm determined it is the last
OL,17,Ftime," he said.
