OL,3,CStormont Health Minister orders pay
OL,4,Cincrease totalling around #200 million
OL,6,F"I've also said on numerous occasions,
OL,7,Fall things being equal, as soon as
OL,8,Fthis year's awards are made public, I
OL,9,Fwould want to action them in full and
OL,10,Fthat's what I've been done, I've just
OL,11,Fsigned this, and will be taking it to
OL,12,Fthe permanent secretary upstairs as
OL,13,Fsoon as we are finished, and that will
OL,14,Fstart a process, and where that goes I
OL,15,Fcannot be sure.
OL,17,F"I think inevitably the permanent
OL,18,Fsecretary will have to say to me, 'you
OL,19,Fcannot afford to do this, so you will
OL,20,Fhave to give me a ministerial
OL,21,Fdirection'.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU
