OL,3,CStormont Health Minister orders pay
OL,4,Cincrease totalling around #200 million
OL,6,F"That, to be clear, is not an event,
OL,7,Fit's part of a process. That
OL,8,Fministerial direction is likely to go
OL,9,Fto a finance minister who may choose
OL,10,Fto implement it, or pass it on to the
OL,11,FExecutive for final decision."
OL,13,FHe added: "I want to pay the workers
OL,14,Fbecause the workforce keeps the health
OL,15,Fservice running ` you need buildings,
OL,16,Fyou need beds, you need equipment, you
OL,17,Fneed medicine. All that is as nothing
OL,18,Fif you don't have the workforce.
