OL,6,F"I am doing what I think is right,
OL,7,Fwhich is to honour the pay parity
OL,8,Fagreements."
OL,10,FDr Alan Stout, chair of the BMA's
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland council, said the 4%
OL,12,F"does not sufficiently address the
OL,13,Fyears of pay erosion", adding that it
OL,14,Fwill be "deeply disappointing for
OL,15,Fdoctors right across Northern Ireland".
