OL,3,CStormont Health Minister orders pay
OL,4,Cincrease totalling around #200 million
OL,6,F"While we welcome the news that the
OL,7,Fminister intends to pay this in full,
OL,8,Fhis comments are some cause for
OL,9,Fconcern in terms of the time it may
OL,10,Ftake to get a final decision on making
OL,11,Fthe award, delaying again the actual
OL,12,Fuplift for members," he said.
OL,14,F"For too long, doctors have faced
OL,15,Fsignificant pay erosion, combined with
OL,16,Fworking in a failing health system
OL,17,Fwhere their jobs have become more
OL,18,Fcomplex and pressured.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@TO]vD@AOU
