OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F443A1747939320
OL,3,CStormont Health Minister orders pay
OL,4,Cincrease totalling around #200 million
OL,6,F"This has had a hugely demoralising
OL,7,Feffect on doctors and has led to
OL,8,Fdoctors choosing to leave the health
OL,9,Fservice or to reduce their contracted
OL,10,Fhours.
OL,12,F"It is imperative that pay keeps pace
OL,13,Fwith the rates offered elsewhere,
OL,14,Fparticularly in the Republic of
OL,15,FIreland, so that we can retain doctors
OL,16,Fin our health system and recruit
OL,17,Fdoctors from elsewhere.
OL,19,F"Our health service is hanging by a
OL,20,Fthread and is running on the goodwill
OL,21,Fof individuals.
